description: The new laboratory at Noble's Hospital is "on track" to start analysing about 200 samples a day.
title: Coronavirus: Isle of Man testing lab 'to open next week'
title_page: Coronavirus: Isle of Man testing lab 'to open next week' - BBC News
maintext: About 200 tests per day are expected to be carried out per day, representing a significant increase from the current average of about 60.
